  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentResult
    Represent a unique Document as a result of a Search in Stanbol
    FacetResult
    Stanbol Facet Result, containing a Solr Facet Field and the type of the Facet.
    FeaturedSearchResult
    Model the result of Stanbol FeaturedSearch service.
    RelatedKeyword
    Representation of a Related Keyword as it is currently modeled in Stanbol.
    SearchResultParser
    This class contains a number of utility methods for parsing both Solr Search and FeaturedSearch service responses to SolrSearchResult and FeaturedSearchResult respectively Also contains methods to transform SolrDocument to DocumentResult that it's the unit representation of a Search Result in the Stanbol Client
    SolrSearchResult
    Model the result of any Stanbol ContentHub Solr Based search.
    StanbolSearchResult
    Abstract class that encapsulates the common information for any kind of Search within Stanbol ContentHub.
    StanbolSolrVocabulary
    Vocabulary class which provides constant properties to be used in the communication with Solr.
